snippet.title: God Eater 3 - PS4/PC - Opening Movie (Trailer)
snippet.description:
The system is about to collapse, the Aragamis are carving a path of destruction… Fight back and break free from your shackles in GOD EATER 3, coming on February 8, 2019 on PS4 and PC!
